      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "AARIELLA'S GIRL (1) is a progressive type who recorded her 9th career win last time out (15.81) at Launceston. Solid record here at the distance winning three races. Recorded the quickest time on the card last start. In sparkling form and looks the one to beat again. ROJO MOLLY (2) is an accomplished sprinter with a great record at the short dashes. Scored over 278m at Launceston last time in a Grade 5 (16.12). Strike rate this distance strong having won three of six tries. Has hit winning form and can measure up again. TIMELESS GRACIE (4) has been a little hard to follow, finishing out of the placings latest but was in winning form two back scoring in a Grade 5 at this track. Well placed here and can atone this time. POLLINATOR KEN (8) was below best last time at this track (19.75) in a Grade 2/3, finishing a 7 length fourth. Has already won two times from this draw.",
